snippet.title: DNF DUEL｜Official Trailer
snippet.description:
#DNFDUEL #TRAILER #던전앤파이터
The Dungeon and Fighter RPG franchise of 16 years is now back as a 2.5D fighting game!
Join the battle as a Berserker, Inquisitor, Striker, Grappler, Ranger, and more!

Check out more information on DNF DUEL through the link below!
Facebook(Global) : https://bit.ly/3chTCji
Facebook(Korean) : https://bit.ly/3ni6Dzw
Twitter(Japanese) : https://twitter.com/DNFDuel
